-- RWE Supervisory Board to Name Tigges Personnel Chief, WAZ
-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 2012-04-16T17:28:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-16/rwe-supervisory-board-to-name-tigges-personnel-chief-waz.html
RWE AG (RWE) ’s supervisory board plans to
appoint Uwe Tigges to the management board,  Westdeutsche
Allgemeine Zeitung  reported, citing people it didn’t name.  Tigges will succeed Alwin Fitting, who will retire from his
position as chief human resources officer in April next year,
the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Randow in Frankfurt at 
 jrandow@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
